Variable Uso <code>product_mapping</code> Dict <code>{item_code: {customer_item_code, customer_item_description, customer_uom}}</code> <ul> <li><code>customer_item_code</code>: del campo <code>ref_code</code> en Item Customer Detail</li> <li><code>customer_item_description</code>: de <code>fm_customer_description</code> (fallback: <code>item_name</code> del item)</li> <li><code>customer_uom</code>: de <code>fm_customer_uom</code> (fallback: código SAT del UOM, ej: <code>H87</code> de <code>H87 - Pieza</code>)</li> </ul> <p>Ejemplo en template: <pre><code>{% set m = product_mapping.get(item.item_code) %}
&lt;gtin&gt;{{ m.customer_item_code if m else item.item_code }}&lt;/gtin&gt;
&lt;invoicedQuantity unitOfMeasure="{{ m.customer_uom if m else item.uom }}"&gt;
</code></pre></p>
